of my colleagues worldwide.


123
00:21:10.670 --> 00:21:14.048
We respect His Holiness' will...

124
00:21:14.132 --> 00:21:18.177
all we ask is his name. Only that!

125
00:21:18.261 --> 00:21:20.429
Tell us if it's one of these 8.

126
00:21:20.514 --> 00:21:23.307
Aguilar? Gregori?

127
00:21:23.433 --> 00:21:27.144
- Bikila? - We believe...
- Todorov?


128
00:21:27.187 --> 00:21:30.272
We believe within a few hours...

129
00:21:30.315 --> 00:21:35.277
the Pontiff will introduce himself
to the faithful from the balcony.


130
00:21:35.320 --> 00:21:37.696
At that point you also will meet him...

131
00:21:37.823 --> 00:21:42.410
