155
00:25:16.625 --> 00:25:18.375
Here it is.

156
00:25:18.418 --> 00:25:20.169
Alright, if it's only for a day...

157
00:25:20.295 --> 00:25:23.631
No cardinal shall have
contact with the outside...


158
00:25:23.673 --> 00:25:26.800
until the election is over...

159
00:25:26.926 --> 00:25:29.428
and publicly announced.

160
00:25:33.683 --> 00:25:37.144
Could I at least get a cappuccino?
Not too hot!


161
00:25:38.813 --> 00:25:43.025
- What will we have?
- Orange juice.


162
00:25:44.903 --> 00:25:47.446
A cappuccino, very little froth.

