207
00:28:45.333 --> 00:28:48.877
- Dreams, yes, though.
- It depends on the dreams.


208
00:28:49.003 --> 00:28:53.382
- However, no... it's best not to.
- Best not to...


209
00:28:53.466 --> 00:28:55.717
Perfect, thank you.

210
00:28:55.760 --> 00:28:57.386
Perfect.

211
00:28:57.470 --> 00:28:59.513
